				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Anthropic makes lots of claims about Claude code, and how well agentic development works for them.  Though a version of the source code was leaked, and there was a lot of critisism on it, their development is not in the open, and it is not available and up to date. They maintain an issue tracker on github however, and that allows us to see more indirectly how they are doing. Experienced engineers have a good intuition about how the issue tracker of a maintainable system looks like. Let's take a look using the cli tooling of github"
			},
			{
				"__type" : "shellCommandSnippet",
				"children" : {
